Hello?

00:21:08.420 --> 00:21:14.460
(Tiantai'an Health Products)

00:21:18.860 --> 00:21:20.200
Coming through. Please step aside.

00:21:20.200 --> 00:21:21.400
Please step aside.

00:21:21.580 --> 00:21:22.430
Seriously.

00:21:22.550 --> 00:21:23.910
It's been sealed off for a while.

00:21:25.480 --> 00:21:26.320
Chief Chen.

00:21:29.160 --> 00:21:30.830
I even bought something from his place.

00:21:36.240 --> 00:21:37.680
This is Ma Weicheng's store.

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:39.830
He usually lived in the back.

00:21:53.590 --> 00:21:55.030
Hair and fingerprints in the house

00:21:55.030 --> 00:21:56.200
have been sent for testing.

00:21:56.200 --> 00:21:57.690
We should get the results by tomorrow.

