And the DNA profile matched

00:23:37.750 --> 00:23:39.440
Qin Hong's record in the database.

00:23:41.510 --> 00:23:43.240
This is the environment
of the crime scene.

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:46.100
(Crime Scene Environment)
On the bedroom wall,

00:23:46.110 --> 00:23:48.920
(On-site Examination)
there were splatter-like blood traces.

00:23:49.310 --> 00:23:51.160
But the wall surface had been damaged.

00:23:51.510 --> 00:23:52.350
We believe

00:23:52.480 --> 00:23:54.310
Qin Hong was likely injured

00:23:54.790 --> 00:23:55.880
by a sharp object here.

