Under the forensic light,
the bloodstains

00:24:01.410 --> 00:24:02.610
confirmed our assumption.

00:24:03.030 --> 00:24:05.030
After Qin Hong fell to the ground,

00:24:05.030 --> 00:24:06.830
she was dragged into the compartment.

00:24:07.160 --> 00:24:08.400
The scene had been wiped down,

00:24:08.550 --> 00:24:09.960
so we couldn't determine

00:24:09.960 --> 00:24:11.400
from the traces alone

