It turns out none of them

00:24:26.640 --> 00:24:27.640
had any records matching

00:24:27.640 --> 00:24:29.310
a patient with that level of blood loss.

00:24:29.750 --> 00:24:31.200
The blood bank also didn't receive

00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:33.110
any blood request of that specific type.

00:24:33.550 --> 00:24:35.120
With such a huge amount of blood loss,

00:24:35.400 --> 00:24:37.680
if she didn't receive
timely medical care

00:24:38.030 --> 00:24:39.550
and an emergency transfusion...

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:44.760
Just say it.

00:24:45.830 --> 00:24:46.790
We believe

00:24:47.310 --> 00:24:48.310
she is

00:24:48.310 --> 00:24:49.150
already dead.

00:24:51.510 --> 00:24:52.440
What was the weapon?

00:24:55.030 --> 00:24:57.440
Inside the toolbox
at the health product store,

00:24:57.960 --> 00:24:59.030
we found a screwdriver.

00:24:59.750 --> 00:25:01.510
There were traces of Qin Hong's blood

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:03.170
and Ma Weicheng's fingerprints.

00:25:05.240 --> 00:25:07.350
We found a large amount of blood
in your home.

00:25:07.920 --> 00:25:09.480
DNA tests confirmed

00:25:09.720 --> 00:25:10.880
it belongs to Qin Hong,

00:25:11.440 --> 00:25:12.480
that is, Lin Chang.

00:25:12.480 --> 00:25:13.320
Officer.

00:25:14.550 --> 00:25:16.400
I honestly have no idea what's going on.

00:25:18.880 --> 00:25:19.790
This screwdriver

00:25:19.790 --> 00:25:22.160
was found in the toolbox at your store.

00:25:22.880 --> 00:25:24.720
There's Qin Hong's blood on it.

00:25:25.480 --> 00:25:26.600
And your fingerprints, too.

00:25:27.350 --> 00:25:28.350
If that's my screwdriver,

00:25:28.350 --> 00:25:29.650
it'd surely have my fingerprints.

00:25:30.070 --> 00:25:31.590
But I really don't know

00:25:31.590 --> 00:25:33.270
why her blood would be on it.

00:25:33.270 --> 00:25:34.680
On the night of Nov. 27,

00:25:34.680 --> 00:25:36.790
someone saw Lin Chang enter your home.

00:25:37.270 --> 00:25:38.240
What were you two doing?

00:25:45.440 --> 00:25:46.310
Having dinner.

00:25:48.550 --> 00:25:49.880
A neighbor said they heard

00:25:49.880 --> 00:25:51.880
arguing and a struggle.

00:25:53.550 --> 00:25:54.390
No way.

00:25:56.070 --> 00:25:56.910
They're wrong.

00:25:58.070 --> 00:25:59.560
That noise didn't come from our place.

00:25:59.910 --> 00:26:00.750
Stop talking.

00:26:00.750 --> 00:26:01.920
She left right after dinner.

00:26:04.480 --> 00:26:05.320
Alright.

00:26:06.000 --> 00:26:07.350
Let's assume she did leave.

00:26:08.000 --> 00:26:09.590
Where did you go after she left?

00:26:09.590 --> 00:26:10.550
I can't remember.

00:26:15.110 --> 00:26:16.510
Then let me help you recall.

00:26:22.620 --> 00:26:25.780
(2013/11/28 Thursday,
Tiantai'an Health Products)

00:26:25.790 --> 00:26:26.630
That's you, right?

00:26:30.350 --> 00:26:31.480
Alone at night,

00:26:31.480 --> 00:26:33.110
you moved a box into your car

00:26:34.110 --> 00:26:35.640
and then drove toward the seaside.

00:26:35.640 --> 00:26:36.480
What were you doing?

00:26:43.920 --> 00:26:45.160
The surveillance never caught

00:26:45.160 --> 00:26:46.750
Lin Chang leaving your house.

00:26:48.510 --> 00:26:50.110
From Nov. 28 onward.

00:26:50.350 --> 00:26:51.720
Lin Chang never showed up again.

00:26:52.310 --> 00:26:54.110
Her clothing store never reopened.

00:26:54.480 --> 00:26:56.000
Are you sure she left?

00:26:58.550 --> 00:26:59.720
Ma Weicheng.

00:27:00.070 --> 00:27:01.240
Tell us the truth.

00:27:02.000 --> 00:27:03.270
Is Lin Chang still alive?

00:27:08.070 --> 00:27:09.590
Your silence won't change a thing.

00:27:10.750 --> 00:27:13.160
This is your chance to confess.

00:27:13.160 --> 00:27:14.510
Answer me honestly.

00:27:14.880 --> 00:27:16.200
- No.
- My medicine.

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:17.880
I didn't kill her.

00:27:17.880 --> 00:27:19.440
Did you kill Lin Chang?

00:27:20.270 --> 00:27:21.480
I didn't kill her.

00:27:21.590 --> 00:27:22.680
I swear it wasn't me.

00:27:25.200 --> 00:27:26.440
If you didn't,

00:27:27.550 --> 00:27:28.680
who did?

00:27:41.000 --> 00:27:42.480
She had a congenital heart disease.

00:27:43.720 --> 00:27:45.070
When we were together,

00:27:45.070 --> 00:27:46.010
she had a few episodes.

00:27:46.200 --> 00:27:47.780
But every time, the medicine cured her.

00:27:50.030 --> 00:27:51.400
That day, she ran out of medicine.

00:27:51.440 --> 00:27:52.280
Wait here.

00:27:52.360 --> 00:27:53.400
I'll go get the medicine.

00:27:53.400 --> 00:27:54.240
Just wait here.

00:27:55.270 --> 00:27:56.470
So, I went to buy it for her.

00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:58.960
By the time I came back,

00:27:59.350 --> 00:28:00.400
she was already gone.

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:06.480
Where's the body?

00:28:12.640 --> 00:28:13.480
Alright.

00:28:14.920 --> 00:28:15.760
Ma Weicheng.

00:28:16.720 --> 00:28:17.930
Let's not waste any more time.

00:28:18.240 --> 00:28:19.550
Since we started questioning you,

00:28:19.550 --> 00:28:20.510
you've given us

00:28:20.510 --> 00:28:22.480
three different versions of your story.

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:25.070
That's proof you're resisting
the interrogation.

00:28:25.480 --> 00:28:27.030
What we found in your house

00:28:27.030 --> 00:28:28.310
was enough to tell us everything.

00:28:28.310 --> 00:28:29.510
It's enough to convict you.

00:28:29.510 --> 00:28:30.920
Let's end the interrogation here.

00:28:31.030 --> 00:28:31.930
Okay? Let's go.

00:28:32.880 --> 00:28:33.720
Officer.

00:28:33.920 --> 00:28:34.760
Officer, Officer.

00:28:36.880 --> 00:28:38.400
If I tell the truth, will you help me?

00:28:59.790 --> 00:29:01.510
I threw her body into the sea.

00:29:07.790 --> 00:29:09.240
We did have a fight that day.

00:29:11.960 --> 00:29:13.510
After she gave me her bank card,

00:29:14.400 --> 00:29:15.610
she wanted to break up with me.

00:29:17.200 --> 00:29:18.240
I asked her why.

00:29:19.750 --> 00:29:21.110
She said she liked someone else.

00:29:22.310 --> 00:29:23.310
I was furious.

00:29:24.200 --> 00:29:25.350
I lost control and hit her.

00:29:27.720 --> 00:29:28.560
My medicine.

00:29:28.830 --> 00:29:29.790
Stop pretending.

00:29:29.790 --> 00:29:31.320
- My medicine.
- After that,

00:29:31.720 --> 00:29:32.920
I went to buy medicine for her,

00:29:34.750 --> 00:29:35.680
as I told you.

00:29:38.270 --> 00:29:40.350
If she died of a heart condition,

00:29:40.790 --> 00:29:42.350
why did you dump the body?

00:29:44.030 --> 00:29:45.070
Because I was scared.

00:29:47.000 --> 00:29:47.840
I couldn't explain

00:29:47.860 --> 00:29:49.440
whether her illness and death

00:29:49.440 --> 00:29:51.640
were connected to me.

00:29:55.960 --> 00:29:57.110
Lin Chang once told me

00:29:59.720 --> 00:30:01.110
that she wanted to escape her past,

00:30:01.110 --> 00:30:02.640
so she came to Pingtan alone.

00:30:05.000 --> 00:30:06.440
I decided to take a chance on that.

00:30:08.480 --> 00:30:10.480
I thought no one would look for her.

00:30:12.200 --> 00:30:14.030
But I honestly had no idea

00:30:14.030 --> 00:30:15.310
whether she'd ever killed someone

00:30:15.310 --> 00:30:17.200
or if she was a wanted murderer.

00:30:18.270 --> 00:30:20.310
As for those photos
you showed me just now,

00:30:20.690 --> 00:30:21.550
I really don't know

00:30:21.550 --> 00:30:22.830
the story behind them.

00:30:22.830 --> 00:30:24.200
I'm telling you the truth.

00:30:30.640 --> 00:30:31.980
There are plenty of contradictions

00:30:31.980 --> 00:30:33.440
between Ma Weicheng's testimony

00:30:33.440 --> 00:30:34.960
and the evidence we found at the scene.

00:30:35.510 --> 00:30:37.110
Though he admitted

00:30:37.110 --> 00:30:38.820
that Qin Hong died
from a heart condition

00:30:38.820 --> 00:30:40.580
after he attacked her,

00:30:40.750 --> 00:30:43.200
it's more likely that Qin Hong

00:30:43.280 --> 00:30:44.640
was violently killed by Ma Weicheng

00:30:44.640 --> 00:30:46.590
based on the evidence we've gathered.

00:30:47.590 --> 00:30:48.840
Reefs are everywhere down there.

00:30:48.840 --> 00:30:50.690
The suitcase Ma Weicheng used
to dump the body

00:30:50.690 --> 00:30:51.990
shouldn't be too hard to locate.

00:30:51.990 --> 00:30:53.440
It's all volcanic rock underneath.

00:30:53.440 --> 00:30:55.480
When the tide comes in,
it's completely submerged.

00:30:55.690 --> 00:30:57.480
The body has been soaking
for over 10 days.

00:30:57.480 --> 00:30:59.720
Most likely, gases have built up inside,

00:30:59.720 --> 00:31:02.070
changing the pressure
inside the suitcase,

00:31:02.070 --> 00:31:04.200
so it might've been swept away
by the current.

00:31:05.510 --> 00:31:07.000
The current?

00:31:09.030 --> 00:31:12.110
Normally, there aren't many people
around here at night.

00:31:12.110 --> 00:31:14.160
But that night, he came rushing in,

00:31:14.160 --> 00:31:16.200
in need of Xin Kang Fu.

00:31:16.830 --> 00:31:17.700
Oh, right.

00:31:17.750 --> 00:31:19.350
I remember he seemed to have a wound

00:31:19.350 --> 00:31:20.190
around this area.

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:22.270
It could be from a recent fight.

00:31:22.720 --> 00:31:24.830
The currents here have their direction.

00:31:24.830 --> 00:31:26.370
A body would drift to a fixed location

00:31:26.370 --> 00:31:27.350
along with the current.

00:31:27.350 --> 00:31:28.830
Our experts are looking into it.

00:31:29.310 --> 00:31:30.510
Is this him?

00:31:31.270 --> 00:31:32.480
To see if it's this person.

00:31:32.480 --> 00:31:34.200
- Yes.
- Ma Weicheng

00:31:34.200 --> 00:31:36.160
did go to buy medicine that night.

00:31:36.830 --> 00:31:37.960
I don't think

00:31:37.960 --> 00:31:39.880
we can believe Ma Weicheng.

00:31:40.110 --> 00:31:42.550
We've questioned him several times,

00:31:42.550 --> 00:31:44.640
and he's always overturned
his previous statements.

00:31:45.310 --> 00:31:46.920
It wasn't until we put the evidence

00:31:46.920 --> 00:31:48.070
right in front of him

00:31:48.070 --> 00:31:50.160
that he realized he couldn't get away

00:31:50.480 --> 00:31:52.130
and finally admitted
to Qin Hong's death.

00:31:52.550 --> 00:31:54.720
So, he's good at dodging the real issue.

00:31:56.270 --> 00:31:57.240
Do you have

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:58.200
erythromycin ointment?

00:31:59.160 --> 00:32:01.750
He only bought Xin Kang Fu,

00:32:01.750 --> 00:32:03.000
not the erythromycin ointment.

00:32:03.000 --> 00:32:04.440
I know. It's for me.

00:32:04.830 --> 00:32:05.680
How much?

00:32:06.400 --> 00:32:07.270
Five yuan.

00:32:07.270 --> 00:32:08.160
Give me two boxes.

00:32:08.160 --> 00:32:09.000
Thanks.

00:32:09.400 --> 00:32:10.250
Thanks.

00:32:10.270 --> 00:32:12.110
We looked into Ma Weicheng before.

00:32:12.110 --> 00:32:13.620
He served three years for fraud.

00:32:13.620 --> 00:32:15.030
(CIU File; Ma Weicheng)
Back then,

00:32:15.030 --> 00:32:16.700
he was running a pretty big company.

00:32:16.700 --> 00:32:17.880
(Jiankanglu Health Technology)

00:32:17.960 --> 00:32:19.680
He tricked a lot of senior citizens

00:32:19.680 --> 00:32:21.200
by selling fake medical equipment.

00:32:23.240 --> 00:32:24.240
So, Ma Weicheng

00:32:24.240 --> 00:32:25.350
is really something.

00:32:25.830 --> 00:32:26.790
From what I see,

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:28.110
he won't tell us the truth

00:32:28.510 --> 00:32:30.110
unless we corner him.

00:32:30.590 --> 00:32:31.640
He definitely knows

00:32:32.240 --> 00:32:33.640
that if we can't find the body,

00:32:33.960 --> 00:32:34.830
we can't determine

00:32:34.830 --> 00:32:36.480
the cause

00:32:36.880 --> 00:32:37.920
of Qin Hong's death.

00:32:38.550 --> 00:32:39.830
And that will directly affect

00:32:40.400 --> 00:32:41.920
his sentence.

00:32:43.270 --> 00:32:45.030
So, we have to locate the body

00:32:45.590 --> 00:32:47.590
to uncover the truth.

00:33:06.310 --> 00:33:07.510
I just came from the bureau.

00:33:08.200 --> 00:33:09.110
Sorry for being late.

00:33:10.920 --> 00:33:12.350
Any updates from the salvage team?

00:33:13.550 --> 00:33:14.720
Nothing for now.

00:33:20.350 --> 00:33:22.110
But the current expert said

00:33:22.750 --> 00:33:24.640
they've found some coordinates.

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:26.400
We've run a field test

00:33:26.790 --> 00:33:28.300
by dumping a box with the same weight

00:33:28.300 --> 00:33:29.260
from the cliff.

00:33:29.400 --> 00:33:31.640
Every time it resurfaced,
it was at those exact spots.

00:33:34.550 --> 00:33:35.720
Then why haven't we found

00:33:35.720 --> 00:33:37.400
the suitcase that held Qin Hong's body?

00:33:41.720 --> 00:33:43.120
After all, it's just an experiment.

00:33:43.120 --> 00:33:44.440
It's not 100% certain.

00:33:45.720 --> 00:33:47.240
But it's helped us narrow things down.

00:33:54.110 --> 00:33:56.030
Have you come across
a similar case before?

00:33:57.440 --> 00:33:58.380
About a year ago, yes.

00:33:58.790 --> 00:33:59.830
Also a body in the sea.

00:34:02.680 --> 00:34:04.000
Did you find the body?

00:34:04.070 --> 00:34:04.910
Yeah.

00:34:06.240 --> 00:34:07.310
A month after the crime,

00:34:08.070 --> 00:34:10.920
the provincial police down south

00:34:10.920 --> 00:34:12.480
found it near the shore.

00:34:22.710 --> 00:34:23.550
Xiaoxiao.

00:34:24.760 --> 00:34:26.780
How much do you know
about the murder case

00:34:26.780 --> 00:34:27.980
in Chencang involving Qin Hong?

00:34:28.030 --> 00:34:29.550
I read all the case reports you sent

00:34:29.550 --> 00:34:30.390
before you came.

00:34:32.920 --> 00:34:33.760
In that case,

00:34:35.230 --> 00:34:37.280
Qin Hong killed for revenge.

00:34:38.280 --> 00:34:40.360
The victim was a major figure

00:34:40.360 --> 00:34:41.670
from the crime gang in Chencang.

00:34:42.590 --> 00:34:43.840
After she killed him,

00:34:43.840 --> 00:34:46.360
Qin Hong managed to evade
the police for a year.

00:34:47.590 --> 00:34:48.650
How could a woman like her

00:34:48.650 --> 00:34:51.210
possibly die at Ma Weicheng's hands?

00:34:56.030 --> 00:34:57.880
I've been thinking
about this these days.

00:34:57.880 --> 00:35:00.320
The Lin Chang that Ma Weicheng described

00:35:00.800 --> 00:35:02.760
is nothing

00:35:02.760 --> 00:35:04.480
like what I would imagine.

00:35:06.800 --> 00:35:08.800
Are you suggesting
that Qin Hong is still alive?

00:35:10.760 --> 00:35:12.360
What if it's just her way

00:35:12.360 --> 00:35:14.880
of escaping the police?

00:35:28.590 --> 00:35:30.480
Why not look at it differently?

00:35:31.000 --> 00:35:32.710
If Qin Hong weren't dead,

00:35:33.400 --> 00:35:34.840
why would Ma Weicheng confess

00:35:34.840 --> 00:35:37.110
during interrogation?

00:35:37.440 --> 00:35:39.280
What possible reason would he have

00:35:39.280 --> 00:35:40.400
to take the fall for Qin Hong

00:35:40.400 --> 00:35:42.480
at the cost of his life and freedom?

00:35:43.510 --> 00:35:44.940
That's the part I can't figure out.

00:35:45.800 --> 00:35:46.780
Unless

00:35:46.780 --> 00:35:47.560
we were both wrong,

00:35:47.560 --> 00:35:48.920
and those two really were in love.

00:35:48.920 --> 00:35:49.880
Then that's possible.

00:36:03.480 --> 00:36:04.360
Maybe it's just hard

00:36:06.230 --> 00:36:07.710
for you to accept This outcome

00:36:07.710 --> 00:36:08.760
right now.

00:36:10.920 --> 00:36:12.280
You've been working on this case

00:36:12.280 --> 00:36:13.760
for more than a year, after all.

00:36:14.190 --> 00:36:16.190
You must've tried every possible way

00:36:16.190 --> 00:36:17.630
and guessed every possible scenario.

00:36:18.230 --> 00:36:19.550
But the result we have now

00:36:20.110 --> 00:36:21.880
is completely beyond what you expected.

